<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-98137" number="24431" version="2099">
			<HEADING>Chapter 13: Petitions for Rulemaking</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17230" name="T06C013"/>Chapter 13: Petitions for Rulemaking</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129893" number="24432" version="2099">
								<HEADING>§ 13-01 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17236" name="T06C013_13-01"/>§ 13-01 Definitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129910" number="24433" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Person.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Person&quot; means a natural person or a business entity, including but not limited to a corporation, trust, estate, partnership, cooperative, association, firm, club or society. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129909" number="24434" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petition.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petition&quot; means a request or application for the Department to adopt a Rule. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129908" number="24435" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petitioner.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petitioner&quot; means the person who files a Petition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129907" number="24436" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Rule.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Rule&quot; shall have the meaning set forth in § 1041 of the City Administrative Procedure Act. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129906" number="24437" version="2099">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 10/8/2021, eff. 11/7/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129912" number="24438" version="2099">
								<HEADING>§ 13-02 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17234" name="T06C013_13-02"/>§ 13-02 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129905" number="24439" version="2099">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any Person may petition the Department to consider the adoption of a Rule. The Petition may be denied if it fails to include the following information: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129904" number="24440" version="2099">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Rule to be considered, with proposed language for adoption; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129903" number="24441" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitioner&apos;s arguments in support of adoption of the Rule; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129902" number="24442" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitioner&apos;s proposal for the time period the Rule should be in effect, if applicable; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129901" number="24443" version="2099">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(4)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The name, address, telephone number, and email address of the Petitioner or his or her authorized representative; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129900" number="24444" version="2099">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(5)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The signature of Petitioner or his or her authorized representative. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129899" number="24445" version="2099">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any change in the name, address or telephone number of the Petitioner or his or her authorized representative must be reported to the Department. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129898" number="24446" version="2099">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>All Petitions should be typewritten, if possible, but handwritten Petitions will be accepted provided they are legible. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129897" number="24447" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitions must be submitted via the email address identified on the Department&apos;s website or by mailing or delivering the Petition to the Department&apos;s Deputy General Counsel, 42 Broadway, 8th Fl., New York, NY 10004. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129896" number="24448" version="2099">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 10/8/2021, eff. 11/7/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129911" number="24449" version="2099">
								<HEADING>§ 13-03 Procedures for Consideration of and Responses to Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17232" name="T06C013_13-03"/>§ 13-03 Procedures for Consideration of and Responses to Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129895" number="24450" version="2497">
									<PARA>If a Petition is submitted in proper form, the Department will deny or approve the Petition within 60 days from the date it was received. The Department will either deny such Petition in a written statement or state in writing the Department&apos;s intention to grant the Petition and to initiate rulemaking by a specified date. The Department is not required to grant the entirety of a Petition and is not bound by the language proposed by Petitioner but may amend or modify such proposed language at the Department&apos;s discretion. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129892" number="24451" version="2099">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 10/8/2021, eff. 11/7/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-066]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>